---
title: Beet and Basil Risotto with Fresh Mozzarella
description: This vibrant risotto is full of incredible flavours! Roasted beets, create a bright and colourful eating experience. Paired with soft creamy mozzerella cheese and fresh basil, dinner tonight is clean, simple and delightful!
